quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Operators [/h1]

[b]Operators[/b] carry out operations on variables and values. [img id="2784" width="100%"]
[h2]Arithmetic Operators[/h2]

Arithmetic operators work with numeric values to perform common arithmetical operations.[img id="2363" width="100%"]
[b]Example:[/b] [code format="php" codeId="469"]<?php
  $num1 = 8;
  $num2 = 6;

  //Addition
  echo $num1 + $num2; //[b]14[/b]

  //Subtraction
  echo $num1 - $num2; //[b]2[/b]

  //Multiplication
  echo $num1 * $num2; //[b]48[/b]

  //Division
   echo $num1 / $num2; //[b]1.33333333333[/b]
?>[/code]

